to a single word I said?

12
00:01:17,625 --> 00:01:20,083
I heard you, and
yet I dare to dream!

13
00:01:20,166 --> 00:01:22,333
That's pretty tame,
as far as dares go.

14
00:01:22,416 --> 00:01:24,666
If we get married,
we'll have even more fun!

15
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:26,250
'Cause It's dangerous
to go alone!

16
00:01:26,333 --> 00:01:27,750
[RUSIAN]
Look. I'm glad you've found

17
00:01:27,833 --> 00:01:30,666
this sudden surge of confidence,
but my answer is still no!

18
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:33,916
[AKO]
Why won't you say yes?!

19
00:01:37,708 --> 00:01:38,875
[RUSIAN]
