to head to the gym!

86
00:05:53,041 --> 00:05:56,208
Have you guys heard? Maeda in
Class 3 told her he loved her.

87
00:05:56,291 --> 00:05:57,500
That dude's brave.

88
00:05:57,583 --> 00:05:58,541
