102
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:44,250
Good morning, everyone.

103
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:46,625
I'm student council
president Goshoin.

104
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:48,541
I'd like to extend
my gratitude to you all

105
00:06:48,625 --> 00:06:50,750
for attending this assembly.

106
00:06:52,333 --> 00:06:54,416
[HIDEKI]
Hi, I'm home!

107
00:07:12,541 --> 00:07:14,666
[HIDEKI] The game that
we play is an MMORPG

108
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:16,458
called <i>Legendary Age</i> .

109
00:07:16,541 --> 00:07:19,333
It gets reduced to <i>LA</i> in most
chat channels and game forums.

110
00:07:19,416 --> 00:07:21,000
It's a way to have
some fun online.

111
00:07:21,083 --> 00:07:23,916
Parts of it cost actual money,
but the core game is free.

112
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,166
With multiple people
accessing it at the same time,

113
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:29,375
we can share in adventures
in this virtual world.

114
00:07:34,208 --> 00:07:35,291
Do it now!

115
00:07:35,375 --> 00:07:37,041
So anyway, I declared
my love on a pier

116
00:07:37,125 --> 00:07:39,500
