sparkling lake.

117
00:07:39,583 --> 00:07:41,333
You mean he made the
girl come out and say it?

118
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:43,250
Wuss doesn't even
begin to describe him.

119
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:44,333
--[APRICOT chuckles]
--[RUSIAN whimpers]

120
00:07:44,416 --> 00:07:45,875
