were barely on the plus side,

134
00:08:27,541 --> 00:08:29,041
so it's no big deal.

135
00:08:29,125 --> 00:08:31,166
[AKO]
Rusian, you're so kind!

136
00:08:31,250 --> 00:08:32,250
